      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "VE"                 to   b-ope                  .
           move      "F"                  to   b-tfe                  .
           move      i-ide-des            to   b-chr                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgv"
                                         using b                      .
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgv"                         .
       exe-pgm-frg-999.
           exit.

