      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Settore gestionale                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      i-ide-set            to   r-ide-set-ges          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fase gestionale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
